Installation tesseract with arabic and english languages

yum-config-manager --add-repo https://download.opensuse.org/repositories/home:/Alexander_Pozdnyakov/RHEL_7/
yum update
yum install tesseract
yum install tesseract-langpack-ara tesseract-langpack-eng